{"tid":2093422,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國駐港總領事 ：對國安法立法失望 表明不會改變與民主派溝通方式","createTime":"2020-07-03T22:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T02:50:38.000Z","uid":28765,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"10a4ee8cc6dc506ff7f4ff60f568fc4e2738fc91","tid":2093422,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T22:06:04.000Z","msg":"港區國安法日前出爐，法例至今未見英文版本，但由駐港國安公署到中央管轄權，以至「勾結外國勢力」條文，都引起美國駐港總領事史墨客（Hanscom Smith）關注，他昨日接受本報訪問時稱，對今次立法感到極之失望（extremely upset），形容條文可怕（terrible），憂慮日後或出現寒蟬效應，但表明不會改變與本地民主派的溝通方式。<br />\n<br />\n明報記者 邱榕瀅<br />\n彭斯：實施國安法背叛國際協議<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n港區國安法條文處處針對「勾結外國勢力」，中央曾多次批評外國干預香港。史墨客否認美國干預香港事務的指控，認為這反映北京對港人欠缺信心，「這似乎是個害怕自己人民的政府」；又指說法是轉移視線，將外國當成代罪羔羊。<br />\n「我們與建制派會面，這是否勾結？」<br />\n<br />\n被問到未來會否改變與本地民主派的溝通方式，史墨客明言「不會」，稱作為外交官，一直按國際慣例行事，「當我們與建制派人士會面，這是否勾結？但會見反對派，為何又會是勾結？」<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20200703/s00001/1593715164100/史墨客-條文可怕-憂現寒蟬-否認美國干預-批北京「似乎害怕人民」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200703%2Fs00001%2F1593715164100%2F%E5%8F%B2%E5%A2%A8%E5%AE%A2-%E6%A2%9D%E6%96%87%E5%8F%AF%E6%80%95-%E6%86%82%E7%8F%BE%E5%AF%92%E8%9F%AC-%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90-%E6%89%B9%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E3%80%8C%E4%BC%BC%E4%B9%8E%E5%AE%B3%E6%80%95%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E3%80%8D&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IKzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=708226f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200703%2Fs00001%2F1593715164100%2F%E5%8F%B2%E5%A2%A8%E5%AE%A2-%E6%A2%9D%E6%96%87%E5%8F%AF%E6%80%95-%E6%86%82%E7%8F%BE%E5%AF%92%E8%9F%AC-%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90-%E6%89%B9%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E3%80%8C%E4%BC%BC%E4%B9%8E%E5%AE%B3%E6%80%95%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E3%80%8D&h=5467a53c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20200703/s00001/1593715164100/史墨客-條文可怕-憂現寒蟬-否認美國干預-批北京「似乎害怕人民」</a>"},{"pid":"15bcc42dad7f4df9791f1fa89a165c7af4e83966","tid":2093422,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T22:08:48.000Z","msg":"親，你已違反國安法38條"},{"pid":"861ff89a60e63dc6feda52b790b4325318ae47ad","tid":2093422,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T23:39:09.000Z","msg":"九成九比國安監聽緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da527647c51785c2a13ed0ad1b28c9589462fbd","tid":2093422,"uid":146621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:35:33.000Z","msg":"邏輯 vs 中國邏輯"},{"pid":"9acc27335906518c23761dce6cd8204d91e538fc","tid":2093422,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:12:30.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5485ec8ab8205f824a8fd95d5721f0eb73ee8957","tid":2093422,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"861ff89a60e63dc6feda52b790b4325318ae47ad","tid":2093422,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T23:39:09.000Z","msg":"九成九比國安監聽緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:23:22.000Z","msg":"國安監聽CIA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84cec9510022a9d0ff50dbf89692dfc4bc7aaa4","tid":2093422,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:25:16.000Z","msg":"又拉得<br />\n正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1bd70ada0a4c2735d16c60352f92c95752e401","tid":2093422,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:25:55.000Z